<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Bulk Student Upload - Admin</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #4f46e5;
        --primary-hover: #4338ca;
        --dark-bg: #111827;
        --card-bg: #1f2937;
        --light-text: #f9fafb;
        --secondary-text: #9ca3af;
        --border-color: #374151;
        --success: #10b981;
        --danger: #ef4444;
        --warning: #f59e0b;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--light-text);
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), #8b5cf6);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .header .breadcrumb {
        background: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .header .breadcrumb-item a {
        color: var(--secondary-text);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .header .breadcrumb-item a:hover {
        color: var(--primary);
      }

      .header .breadcrumb-item.active {
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1rem;
      }

      .card {
        background-color: var(--card-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .card-title {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .info-box {
        background-color: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid var(--primary);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .info-box h3 {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      .info-box ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--secondary-text);
      }

      .info-box ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .info-box code {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .form-label {
        color: var(--light-text);
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .form-control {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        color: var(--light-text);
        padding: 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .form-control:focus {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        border-color: var(--primary);
        color: var(--light-text);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
      }

      .form-control::file-selector-button {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-right: 1rem;
      }

      .form-control::file-selector-button:hover {
        background-color: var(--primary-hover);
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        border: none;
        color: white;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: var(--primary-hover);
      }

      .btn-outline-light {
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .btn-outline-light:hover {
        background-color: var(--border-color);
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .btn-success {
        background-color: var(--success);
        border: none;
      }

      .btn-success:hover {
        background-color: #059669;
      }

      .alert {
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border: none;
      }

      .alert-danger {
        background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid var(--danger);
        color: #fca5a5;
      }

      .alert-success {
        background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid var(--success);
        color: #6ee7b7;
      }

      .error-list {
        max-height: 300px;
        overflow-y: auto;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
      }

      .error-list ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
      }

      .error-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .stats-container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .stat-box {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .stat-box .stat-value {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--primary);
      }

      .stat-box .stat-label {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--secondary-text);
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
      }

      .sample-table {
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }

      .sample-table th {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        padding: 0.5rem;
        text-align: left;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      }

      .sample-table td {
        padding: 0.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        color: var(--secondary-text);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1><i class="fas fa-users-cog"></i> Bulk Student Upload</h1>
      <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumb">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/admin">Admin Dashboard</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">
            Bulk Student Upload
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <!-- Success Message -->
      <% if (successMsg) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-success">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <%= successMsg %> <% if (details) {
        %>
        <div class="stats-container">
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-value"><%= details.total %></div>
            <div class="stat-label">Total Rows</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-value" style="color: var(--success)">
              <%= details.success %>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-label">Created</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-value" style="color: var(--warning)">
              <%= details.skipped %>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-label">Skipped</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <% } %>

      <!-- Error Messages -->
      <% if (errorMsg && Array.isArray(errorMsg)) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-danger">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
        <strong>Errors encountered:</strong>
        <div class="error-list">
          <ul>
            <% errorMsg.forEach(function(error) { %>
            <li><%= error %></li>
            <% }); %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% } else if (errorMsg) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-danger">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> <%= errorMsg %>
      </div>
      <% } %>

      <!-- Instructions Card -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">
          <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Instructions
        </h2>

        <div class="info-box">
          <h3>CSV Format Requirements</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Required Columns:</strong> <code>email</code>,
              <code>usn</code>, <code>department</code>, <code>semester</code>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Optional Columns:</strong> <code>fname</code>,
              <code>lname</code>, <code>phone</code>, <code>imageurl</code>
            </li>
            <li>CSV must have a header row with column names</li>
            <li>
              Department codes: cs, is, ec, et, ai, cv, ee, ad (lowercase)
            </li>
            <li>Semester must be between 1 and 8</li>
            <li>USN format: <code>1BY22CS001</code></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <a href="/admin/download-student-template" class="btn btn-success">
            <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download Sample CSV Template
          </a>
        </div>

        <details style="margin-top: 1rem">
          <summary
            style="cursor: pointer; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600"
          >
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i> View Sample CSV Format
          </summary>
          <table class="sample-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>email</th>
                <th>usn</th>
                <th>department</th>
                <th>semester</th>
                <th>fname</th>
                <th>lname</th>
                <th>phone</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>student1@example.com</td>
                <td>1BY22CS001</td>
                <td>cs</td>
                <td>1</td>
                <td>John</td>
                <td>Doe</td>
                <td>9876543210</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>student2@example.com</td>
                <td>1BY22CS002</td>
                <td>cs</td>
                <td>1</td>
                <td>Jane</td>
                <td>Smith</td>
                <td>9876543211</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </details>
      </div>

      <!-- Upload Form Card -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">
          <i class="fas fa-upload"></i> Upload Student Data
        </h2>

        <form
          action="/admin/addbulckstudent"
          method="POST"
          enctype="multipart/form-data"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="csvFile" class="form-label">
              <i class="fas fa-file-csv"></i> Select CSV File *
            </label>
            <input
              type="file"
              class="form-control"
              id="csvFile"
              name="csvFile"
              accept=".csv"
              required
            />
            <small class="text-muted">Maximum file size: 5MB</small>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="password" class="form-label">
              <i class="fas fa-key"></i> Default Password for All Students *
            </label>
            <input
              type="password"
              class="form-control"
              id="password"
              name="password"
              placeholder="Enter a common password for all students"
              minlength="6"
              required
            />
            <small class="text-muted"
              >Minimum 6 characters. All students will use this password to
              login.</small
            >
          </div>

          <div class="d-flex gap-2">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
              <i class="fas fa-upload"></i> Upload and Create Accounts
            </button>
            <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-outline-light">
              <i class="fas fa-times"></i> Cancel
            </a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Notes Card -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">
          <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Important Notes
        </h2>
        <ul style="color: var(--secondary-text); line-height: 1.8">
          <li>
            All students created via bulk upload will be
            <strong>automatically approved</strong> (userallowed = true)
          </li>
          <li>
            Email verification will be <strong>skipped</strong> for bulk
            uploaded students
          </li>
          <li>
            Students can login immediately using their email and the password
            you set
          </li>
          <li>
            Duplicate emails or USNs will be skipped with an error message
          </li>
          <li>The system will extract the year from the USN automatically</li>
          <li>Process will continue even if some rows have errors</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
